Create Portal	CATEGORY:FEAT	TYPE:ItemCreation	VISIBLE:YES				PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Craft Wondrous Item																		DESC:You can create any portal whose prerequisites you meet. Crafting a portal takes one day for each 1000 gp in its base price. To craft a portal, you must spend 1/25 of its base price in XP and use up raw materials costing half of this base price. Se Chapter 2: Magic for details of portal creation. Some portals incur extra costs in material components or XP as noted in their descriptions. These costs are in addition to those derived from the portal's base price.																	SOURCEPAGE:FRCS30					
